snippet.title: Thunder Rally Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Thunder Rally on Steam! http://bit.ly/ThunderRally

Thunder Rally is a party game with crazy physics, hazardous environments, drivers getting run over by cars, drivers punching cars over, and explosive barrels launched by defeated players.

Visit our website or follow us on Twitter for more information and updates:
http://www.typicalentertainment.com/
https://twitter.com/Typical_Ent
